OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA man who subjected a woman to eight
OL,8,Fyears of repeated emotional and
OL,9,Fphysical abuse has been jailed.
OL,11,FBetween 2017 and 2025, Ernie Jones
OL,12,Ffrom Godalming, Surrey had punched and
OL,13,Fkicked the victim in the face, stamped
OL,14,Fon the victim's head, and threatened
OL,15,Fher with a knife.
OL,17,FHis abuse also included damaging the
OL,18,Fvictim's property, including her
OL,19,Fphone, and verbal abuse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
