CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHe would prevent the victim from
OL,8,Fseeing their children, threatening to
OL,9,Ftake them away or put them into care
OL,10,Fand making false reports of child
OL,11,Fneglect to social services.
OL,13,FIn February last year, Jones was
OL,14,Fdriving the victim's car whist she was
OL,15,Fsat in the passenger seat with their
OL,16,Fchildren in the back.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
