PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FIn a disagreement over brambles to the
OL,8,Fside of the road causing damage to the
OL,9,Fvehicle, Jones began beating the
OL,10,Fvictim whilst stopped at traffic
OL,11,Flights.
OL,13,FIn May, police officers were called to
OL,14,Fan address where the victim revealed
OL,15,Fshe had suffered eight years of
OL,16,Fphysical and psychological domestic
OL,17,Fabuse at the hands of Jones.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
