PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FJones was arrested the following day
OL,8,Fand released on conditional bail.
OL,9,FHowever, Jones was in breach of his
OL,10,Fconditions on several occasions, with
OL,11,Frepeated unwanted contact amounting to
OL,12,Fa charge for stalking.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
