PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FReflecting on the abuse, the survivor
OL,8,Fshared: "For eight years, I lived
OL,9,Funder Ernie's control and abuse. This
OL,10,Fwas not a misunderstanding. It was not
OL,11,Fa handful of isolated incidents. It
OL,12,Fwas a deliberate and repeated pattern
OL,13,Fof behaviour, choices he made, that
OL,14,Fslowly and systematically stripped
OL,15,Faway my independence, my confidence,
OL,16,Fand my sense of who I was.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
