OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"I lived in constant fear. Fear of his
OL,8,Fmoods, fear of his reactions, fear of
OL,9,Fsaying the wrong word or making the
OL,10,Fwrong decision. I was always walking
OL,11,Fon eggshells.
OL,13,F"Over time, I stopped feeling like a
OL,14,Fperson in my own right. I felt like I
OL,15,Fexisted only to serve Ernie, to meet
OL,16,Fhis needs before my own, to keep him
OL,17,Fcalm, to prevent his anger. I felt
OL,18,Flike a slave in my own life. I felt
OL,19,Fworthless and degraded."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
