FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F29-year-old Jones was sentenced at
OL,8,FGuildford Crown Court on 10 April for
OL,9,Ftwo counts of controlling and coercive
OL,10,Fbehaviour (CCB), actual bodily harm,
OL,11,Fand stalking with fear of violence.
OL,13,FHe was sentenced to seven years and
OL,14,Ftwo months in prison, with a
OL,15,Frestraining order until further notice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
