PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FDC Emily Heath led the domestic abuse
OL,8,Finvestigation and worked with the
OL,9,Fsurvivor to achieve the successful
OL,10,Foutcome. Emily said: "The survivor has
OL,11,Fshown tremendous courage in reporting
OL,12,Fthe abuse and supporting the
OL,13,Finvestigation throughout. Despite
OL,14,Fexperiencing abusive, violent and
OL,15,Fintimidating behaviour.
OL,17,F"No one should be treated this way in
OL,18,Fa relationship. I commend her bravery
OL,19,Fin coming forward and hope she can now
OL,20,Fbegin to rebuild her life after this
OL,21,Ftraumatic experience.
OL,26,@rD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
