OL,3,CMan who abused woman for eight years,
OL,4,Cincluding stamping on her head, is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"I would also like to recognise the
OL,8,Fvital support provided to the victim
OL,9,Fby our Domestic Abuse Caseworker and
OL,10,Fpartner outreach services, whose
OL,11,Fprofessionalism, care and practical
OL,12,Fassistance have helped ensure she has
OL,13,Fbeen supported throughout and provided
OL,14,Fexcellent care and advice in
OL,15,Fnavigating a way to re-start her life."
OL,17,FLinks to support can be found here.
